title: IObit Advanced SystemCare 10 RC PRO v10.0.2.359 Multilingual
description:
IObit Advanced SystemCare 10 RC PRO v10.0.2.359 Multilingual (2016)



Install Notes:

Install application
Register application with given serial.
Done, Enjoy. 



Advanced SystemCare provides automated and all-in-one PC care service with Malware Removal, Registry Fix, Privacy Protection, Performance Tune-up, and System Cleaning capabilities. It also creates superior and safer online experience with the latest Surfing Protection and Internet Boost technology, ensuring you top online security and maximum PC performance.


What's New in Advanced SystemCare 10 RC:

+ Redesigned FaceID - Supported adding more face models of different positions to improve recognition. And enhanced FaceID for more stable performance.
+ Improved Surfing Protection & Ads Removal - Block more malicious websites and remove more annoying ads.
+ More Powerful Uninstalling - Supported uninstalling more stubborn programs & browser toolbars and removing more malicious & ad-based plug-ins with new IObit Uninstaller 6.
+ Larger Database - Expanded database for Spyware Removal, Startup Manager, and Privacy Sweep.
+ Improved Performance Monitor - More accurate temperature and disk data.
+ Enhanced Screenshot - Improved the quality of saved screenshots.
+ Added 22 multiple languages.
+ Many performance & GUI improvements.
Fixed bugs in previous version
